# README

Welcome to my Website project! This repository is intended to back up and track the progress of my website, protecting it from data loss due to unexpected issues.

## Project Structure

The project is organized into three main folders:

- **pages**: Contains all HTML5 files.
- **styles**: Contains all CSS files, organized by property.
- **functions**: Contains JavaScript or other functional code.

Feel free to explore each folder to understand how the website is structured.
